                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5417" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0809</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8525 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">生存还是毁灭：安洁科技“商誉变利润”迷局</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">To be or Not to be: ANJIE Technology&#39;s Puzzle of &quot;change goodwill into profit&quot;</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">蒋弘，陈钰，余娇，杨莲</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">重庆工商大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">苏州安洁科技股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">电子工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">安洁科技；溢价并购；商誉减值；业绩承诺</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ANJIE Technology; premium M &amp; A; goodwill impairment; performance commitment</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019年，是上市公司商誉集中爆雷的一年，数百家上市公司因为大额的商誉减值纷纷业绩变脸，给企业带来巨大风险。本案例描述了安洁科技上市后为了转型走上并购之路，花70亿并购多家公司，其中又以三次大手笔并购最为突出，只不过是雷声大雨点小，三家公司业绩完全不达标，安洁科技似乎当了“冤大头”。但是在这三次并购中，安洁科技签订了两个业绩承诺协议，正是由于这两个协议，2018年成功帮助企业扭亏为盈，不过2019年，超过20亿的业绩补偿也没能抵挡住商誉爆雷的颓势，企业迎来了上市后的首次亏损。案例分析了业绩补偿与商誉减值之间的博弈，旨在提醒上市公司不要盲目高溢价并购，也不要被高额业绩承诺所引诱而为企业埋下商誉暴雷的隐患。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In 2019, the goodwill of listed companies will explode intensively. Hundreds of listed companies will change their performance one after another because of the large amount of goodwill impairment, which will bring huge risks to enterprises. This case describes that in order to transform and embark on the road of M &amp; A after ANJIE Technology went public, it spent 7 billion yuan on M &amp; A of many companies, among which three large-scale M &amp; A were the most prominent, but it’s much cry and little wool, the performance of the three companies was not up to standard, so ANJIE Technology seemed to be the &quot;wastrel&quot;. However, in these three cases, ANJIE Technology signed two performance commitment agreements. It is precisely because of these two agreements that it successfully helped the enterprise turn losses into profits in 2018. However, in 2019, more than 2 billion performance compensation failed to resist the decline of goodwill explosion, and the enterprise ushered in its first loss after listing. This paper analyzes the game between performance compensation and goodwill impairment, aiming to remind listed companies not to blindly merge with high premium, nor to be lured by high performance commitment to bury the hidden danger of goodwill thunder for enterprises.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业并购与重组》、《财务管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">商誉的计量与减值</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021-06</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
